\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 And this says nothing of the difference between a human copying their work because they are inspired, and an AI model copying their work because there is an economic incentive. Imitation is the sincerest form of flattery\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 unless you\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92re trying to supplant the original.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 In my own personal experience, I was 21 when I realized I was an absolute hack and was just aping other people\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s art, and had a bit of a mental breakdown over it. It\u8217\'92s been many years since then, and I\u8217\'92ve been richly rewarded for putting in the effort to go my own way, to find my own creative solutions to .}
\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0
