\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The most important is that this position views art solely as an economic product, when it isn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 There is, however, a segment of the industry which it will replace.}
