\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Art belongs to the category of words which label methods for exploring existence. Science, religion, among them. The difference between them lies in the method used for exploration - science employs scientific method, religion employs revelation/spiritual experience, art employs the making of an object. The difference between artist and the craftsman is the difference between the scientist and the engineer, or the prophet and the priest - one is exploring, the other are memorizing signs and symbols and repeating them for effect.}}